title: The Ultimate Oldskool Mix Collection
description:
Three CD-length mixes of UK oldskool hardcore and rave from the early 90s.  Each mix is provided as individual tracks as well as a full length DJ mix.

If you liked these mixes check out these:

The Ultimate Happy Hardcore Mix Collection - http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3758337/The_Ultimate_Happy_Hardcore_Mix_Collection
The Ultimate Trance Mix Collection - http://thepiratebay.se/tor/3742378/The_Ultimate_Trance_Mix_Collection
